33:42.888 --> 33:44.848
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:44.848 --> 33:47.309
<i>Forged it from</i>
<i>a nice, big chunk of W2.</i>

33:47.309 --> 33:50.103
<i>Copper guard,</i>
<i>the walnut handle.</i>

33:50.103 --> 33:52.939
<i>I think it's gonna be,</i>
<i>uh, pretty nice.</i>

33:52.939 --> 33:55.358
- Brian,
how did things go for you?

33:55.358 --> 33:56.943
- I started out a little shaky,

33:56.943 --> 33:59.154
