33:59.154 --> 34:01.239
<i>but I'm super happy with it.</i>

34:01.239 --> 34:03.074
<i>Uh, put a little bit</i>
<i>of engraving,</i>

34:03.074 --> 34:04.951
<i>a lacewood handle.</i>

34:04.951 --> 34:06.661
- All right, gentlemen,
your weapons will now be put

34:06.661 --> 34:08.413
through a series
