a sharpness test,

34:09.915 --> 34:12.375
and, up first, the kill test.

34:12.375 --> 34:13.793
Doug?

34:13.793 --> 34:16.379
<i>♪ ♪</i>

34:16.379 --> 34:19.841
- Welcome to
our kilij kill test.

34:19.841 --> 34:21.843
- [chuckles]

34:21.843 --> 34:23.345
- To see what kinda lethal
damage your weapon will do,

34:23.345 --> 34:25.555
I will take your kilij
and deliver killing blows

34:25.555 --> 34:27.515
to this large side of beef.

34:27.515 --> 34:28.892
Let's see how deadly
your weapons are.

34:28.892 --> 34:30.685
- [exhales]

34:30.685 --> 34:32.020
- Connor, you're up first.
You ready?

34:32.020 --> 34:34.022
- I don't know.
