34:46.034 --> 34:48.620
<i>♪ ♪</i>

34:48.620 --> 34:51.831
<i>[rock music]</i>

34:51.831 --> 34:57.879
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:03.301 --> 35:04.678
Nice.

35:04.678 --> 35:06.179
<i>[tense music]</i>

35:06.179 --> 35:07.556
[exhales]

35:07.556 --> 35:09.766
- Connor, your blade is sharp.

35:09.766 --> 35:13.019
This lacerates deep into
that meat carcass.

35:13.019 --> 35:15.480
One issue I had a little bit
was with the handle.

35:15.480 --> 35:17.857
On the first impact,
I felt it rotate,

35:17.857 --> 35:19.985
so I had to adjust with it.

35:19.985 --> 35:23.613
But this, sir, will kill.

35:23.613 --> 35:26.366
- Thank you, sir.

35:26.366 --> 35:28.034
- Brian, you're up next.
