35:28.034 --> 35:30.078
- Absolutely. Let's go.
- Let's do this.

35:30.078 --> 35:35.333
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:38.503 --> 35:41.423
<i>[rock music]</i>

35:41.423 --> 35:47.137
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:53.476 --> 35:55.228
- Nice.
- Sweet.

