both: Yeah.

35:56.605 --> 35:58.898
<i>[tense music]</i>

35:58.898 --> 36:00.984
- First off the bat,

36:00.984 --> 36:03.069
that's a sharp blade.

36:03.069 --> 36:05.989
It's so curved over here
with the balance being forward,

36:05.989 --> 36:08.491
