that digs in

36:08.491 --> 36:11.369
and continues to cut
as I'm drawing the blade.

36:11.369 --> 36:12.537
The handle feels good
in the hand,

36:12.537 --> 36:14.247
to where I can index

36:14.247 --> 36:16.458
and tell where it is
cutting all the time.

36:16.458 --> 36:19.210
It will kill.
- Nice. Excellent. Thank you.

36:19.210 --> 36:21.796
- Next up, the strength test.

36:21.796 --> 36:24.174
J-minator?

36:24.174 --> 36:26.468
- Okay.
- This is gonna be fun.

36:26.468 --> 36:28.178
- [laughs]
- Here we go.

36:28.178 --> 36:29.721
- Tons of fun.

36:29.721 --> 36:31.056
- As you see,
we've got some nice,

36:31.056 --> 36:33.016
sturdy oak barrels over here,

