<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:57.374 --> 36:59.668
- [grunting]

36:59.668 --> 37:02.629
<i>[rock music]</i>

37:02.629 --> 37:06.091
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:06.091 --> 37:07.884
<i>[tense music]</i>

37:07.884 --> 37:09.135
- [exhales]

37:09.135 --> 37:10.762
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:10.762 --> 37:12.555
- Ooh...
- [chuckles]

37:12.555 --> 37:15.016
- Connor, we got
a couple problems here.

37:15.016 --> 37:18.186
Your blade torqued out...

37:18.186 --> 37:20.438
