<i>♪ ♪</i>

38:14.534 --> 38:16.035
- Oh...

38:16.035 --> 38:18.997
<i>[tense music]</i>

38:18.997 --> 38:21.082
<i>♪ ♪</i>

38:21.082 --> 38:22.876
- All right, Brian.

