On the plus side,

38:34.137 --> 38:35.847
your edge is still razor sharp.

38:35.847 --> 38:37.265
- Thanks.

38:37.265 --> 38:40.059
<i>♪ ♪</i>

38:40.059 --> 38:41.936
- Gentlemen, your blades
have made it through

38:41.936 --> 38:44.564
