40:53.484 --> 40:54.903
and that's why
we're sending you home.

40:54.903 --> 40:56.696
- Understood. Thank you.

40:56.696 --> 40:58.573
- Brian, please surrender
your blade.

40:58.573 --> 40:59.699
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:59.699 --> 41:02.035
<i>- It was close,</i>

41:02.035 --> 41:04.037
<i>but at the end of the day,</i>
